                  {
                    "cta": "Next!",
                    "text": "Hey! Today we will learn how to speak confidently in client meetings.\nYou will learn how to give project updates and present your work.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/4d69ca61-4c89-4499-95a4-492b22053c76-client-meeting---2-(1).jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Got it!",
                    "text": "To share progress on tasks, say:\n\"We've finished [task] and now we're working on [task].\"\nExample: \"We've finished the payment setup and now we're working on the dashboard.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/4d69ca61-4c89-4499-95a4-492b22053c76-client-meeting---2-(1).jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Nice!",
                    "text": "To show something to the client, say:\n\"Let me show you [item] quickly.\"\nExample: \"Let me show you the wireframes quickly.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/4d69ca61-4c89-4499-95a4-492b22053c76-client-meeting---2-(1).jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "I see!",
                    "text": "To talk about what is on time and what needs more time, say:\n\"We're on track with [task], but [task] needs more time.\"\nExample: \"We're on track with the backend, but testing needs more time.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/4d69ca61-4c89-4499-95a4-492b22053c76-client-meeting---2-(1).jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Start Practice!",
                    "text": "Now let's practice using these in a client meeting!",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/4d69ca61-4c89-4499-95a4-492b22053c76-client-meeting---2-(1).jpg",
                      "type": "image"
